| TDATA31 | -TDATA4 |
| TDATA32 | -TDATA5 |
| TDATA33 | 0 |
| TDATA34 | 0 |
| TDATA35 | 0 |
| TDATA36 | 1 |
| TDATA37 | TDATA9 |
| TDATA38 | TDATA11 |
| TDATA39 | 0 |
| TDATA40 | A elegir. |
| TDATA41 | 0 |
| TDATA42 | 0 |
| TDATA43 | 0 |
| TDATA44 | 0 |
| TDATA45 | 0 |
| TDATA46 | 0 |
| TDATA47 | 0 |
| TDATA48 | 0 |
| TDATA49 | 1 |
| TDATA50 | A elegir. |
| TDATA51 | A elegir. |
| TDATA52 | A elegir. |
"""@es .

